<h2 id="markdown-file">Markdown file</h2>

<p>Remember to add</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>---
# front matter as to store the data for your page/site
title: home
layout: default
---
# HEADER 1
## HEADER 2

Lorem
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>layout default will get the default.html in your _layouts folder and generate a page out of that for you.
bellow front matter is the start of content for your page as in &lt;h1 id="edge-augustana-web-guild-coding-projects"&gt;EDGE Augustana Web Guild Coding Projects&lt;/h1&gt;</p>

