<h2 id="for-loop-loading-posts">For loop loading posts</h2>

<p>example for my coding page.
in my posts md front matter I added <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">categories: [coding]</code> to list all post in the categories array.</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"gallery"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
