<h2 id="launch-project-on-github">Launch project on github</h2>

<p>Change or make sure your repo name is [yourgithubaccount].github.io</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git add .
git commit -m"Created project"
git push
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Go to Setting and scroll down to Github page.
Launch the page by choosing the main branch.
Check the project!</p>
